title: Google Ears v1.8 (What's this song?) for any country...
description:
So this is Google Ear's widget "What's this song", this is re-compiled and re-signed to keep this unfrozen in UNSUPPORTED countries like e.g. in Estonia and in Finland..

This won't work in ARMv6 devices and on Gingerbread or older..
This works on Honeycomb, Ice Cream Sandwich and Jelly Bean!


This is from my thread in XDA developers.


How to install:

Just install as normal app by opening an .apk file and then pressing "install", then go to Widgets section and drag What's this song? widget into home screen!
